special_powers.description: STOP. Devil Dinosaur can use Battle Fury. Devil Dinosaur can't be healed above this click for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: AUTOMATONS OF H.A.T.E.
special_powers.description: Drop Bear's move actions don't count against your action total.

special_powers.name: MENTALLY CONTROLLED TENTACLES
special_powers.description: When he makes a close combat attack Doctor Octopus can use Giant Reach: 3 and Improved Targeting: Characters. Give him a power action to make 4 close combat attacks that deal 2 damage. After actions resolve modify the defense value of any character hit more than 2 times by these attacks by -2 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SINISTER MASTERMIND
special_powers.description: Doctor Octopus can use Leadership and Outwit. During your turn up to 2 adjacent friendly characters with the Sinister Syndicate keyword can be given a power action to use Outwit.

special_powers.name: I COULD BE ANYONE
special_powers.description: When building your force, you may include up to 3 standard characters of 60 points or less on your Sideline. These characters are Disguises this game. Disguises can't be replaced or chosen for any game effects unless used by Chameleon.

special_powers.name: MASTER OF DISGUISES
special_powers.description: Give Chameleon a power action if no opposing character has line of fire to him. Replace him with a Disguise the same number of clicks from its starting line. For the rest of the game, any time that character is targeted with an attack, roll a d6. On a result of 1-4 that character is no longer a Disguise and is replaced by Chameleon the same number of clicks from his starting line and he becomes the target of the attack. This can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: I KNOW WHO YOU REALLY ARE, SPIDER-MAN!
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 3 squares can't use Shape Change or be replaced.

special_powers.name: MALLEABLE FACE
special_powers.description: Chameleon can use Shape Change, Stealth, and is a wildcard.

special_powers.name: GOD OF WAR
special_powers.description: Ares can't be targeted by Outwit or Probability Control from opposing characters unless the targeting character has a higher point value or has the Deity keyword.

special_powers.name: CRIPPLING BLOWS
special_powers.description: When an opposing character takes damage from a close attack from Ares, attach the Slash marker to that character, removing it from anywhere else. When a character with the Slash marker is given an action token, deal it 1 penetrating damage. When that character heals or clears action tokens, remove the Slash marker.

special_powers.name: RELENTLESS
special_powers.description: When Ares KO's an opposing character, remove an action token from him and heal him 1 click.

special_powers.name: DRAINING YOUR LIFE
special_powers.description: Morlun begins the game on click #4. When an opposing character takes damage from a close attack from Morlun, attach the Slash marker to that character, removing it from anywhere else. When a character with the slash marker is given an action token, deal it one penetrating damage. When that character heals or clears action tokens, remove the Slash marker.

special_powers.name: TO FEED MINE
special_powers.description: Morlun can use Steal Energy. When he does, if the opposing character that took damage has the Animal or Spider-Man Family keyword, heal him 2 clicks instead. When an opposing character takes damage from his Slash marker, heal him one click. When he heals in any of these ways, he may heal past his starting line.

special_powers.name: APPEARING ANYWHERE IN THE MULTIVERSE THE TOTEMS ARE
special_powers.description: Morlun can use Phasing/Teleport and Sidestep. Give Morlun a free action and place him adjacent to an opposing character within 8 squares that has the Animal or Spider-Man family keyword.

special_powers.name: CALL IN HELP FROM THE SPIDER-VERSE!
special_powers.description: Once per turn for all characters with this trait, when Spider-Man 2211 hits an opposing character, after actions resolve you may roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. 3 - 6: Place another friendly character with the Spider-Man Family keyword adjacent to this character.

special_powers.name: SPIDER'S WEB
special_powers.description: When Spider-Man 2211 hits, after actions resolve you may attach his Web marker to a hit target, removing it from anywhere else. That character with the Web marker can't move without breaking away and can't automatically break away. Other characters don't have to break away from that character. When that character successfully breaks away, remove the Web marker.

special_powers.name: TIMESPINNERS, GUARDIANS OF THE TIMELINE
special_powers.description: Spider-Man 2211 can use Probability Control.  He can use it to reroll the attack rolls of characters that can use Probability Control regardless of range and line of fire.

special_powers.description: Equipped character can use Plasticity and Shape Change, and automatically breaks away. Give the equipped character a free action and roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. 5-6: Modify this characters combat values by +1 until your next turn. 1: Place this object in an adjacent square and the last equipped character can't be equipped by it again this game.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Equipped character can use Leap/Climb, and may be given a ranged combat action to make a range attack with a range value of 4 that deals no damage. When equipped character hits with this attack, after actions resolve you may attach a Web marker to a hit target, removing it from anywhere else. That character with the Web marker can't move without breaking away and can't automatically break away. Other characters don't have to break away from that character. When that character successfully breaks away, remove the Web marker.
